    • Method Detail

      • start

        void start(UpdateLayer layer)
        Called when the MaplyUpdateLayer is initialized. This is called after things are set up. You'll be on the layer thread here.

      • viewerMovedTo

        void viewerMovedTo(UpdateLayer layer,
                   ViewState viewState)
        Called when the viewer moves. You'll be called on the layer thread when the viewer moves more than your moveDist, subject to calls no more frequent than the minTime.

      • teardown

        void teardown(UpdateLayer layer)
        Called when the update layer is shutting down. Clean up your own data here.
